Name: Sharain
AboutMe:
Greetings. My name is Christoffer. I live in Norway where I was born in the 90's. Fine year, that one! I work as an IT-apprentice for a company with a reasonably large server system. Computers and phones are common tools here.

I know a bit about that, nothing I am "pro" in, but I am always glad to try my best to help with an issue.

We learn from our mistakes, and that is a fact no one can deny. I've learned a lot trough trial and error.

In my free time I draw and play computer games, mostly FPS. I do at times also dwell with magic the gathering, the card game. Beyond that there is not much to say, but I'll gladly answer any questions you might have!

Also, I like those Ponies. Yes, I am one of them. So? Anyhow, Fluttershy is most adorable pony!

Cheers!
